00:10:47.927 --> 00:10:49.206
ir't im zogn,

00:10:49.206 --> 00:10:50.882
az ikh hob aykh gezogt,..."

00:10:51.471 --> 00:10:57.557
mir ze'mir ts- azoy gegangen. m'iz tsugekumen, getrofn dem hiter, un der hiter hot ongeklungen tsu zey, un m'hot geheysn undz araynlozn.

00:10:57.732 --> 00:10:59.228
m'iz arayngekumen.

00:10:59.571 --> 00:11:01.019
undz avekgezetst.

00:11:01.019 --> 00:11:03.631
m'hot undz avekgeshtelt a groyse shisl esn.

00:11:04.195 --> 00:11:05.775
m'hot opgegesn.

00:11:06.321 --> 00:11:07.884
dernokh dem hot er gezogt,

00:11:08.582 --> 00:11:09.903
"vos bistu?"

00:11:09.903 --> 00:11:14.499
hot er gezogt, eyner hot gezogt, er iz a shnayder. der hot gezogt, er iz a shuster. eyner hot gezogt, er iz a katsev.

00:11:14.623 --> 00:11:16.203
ikh hob gezogt az ikh bin a

00:11:16.615 --> 00:11:17.976
TISCHLER, a stolyer.

00:11:18.484 --> 00:11:19.410
"gut," zogt er.

00:11:19.534 --> 00:11:22.835
"ir't farrikhtn di shtivl, ir't farrikhtn dos ontun."

00:11:24.073 --> 00:11:27.121
un m'hot undz gegibn a, geheysn makhn zikh aza min,

00:11:28.123 --> 00:11:29.436
⟨a, a,⟩ vi a palatke,

00:11:29.436 --> 00:11:31.273
fun di, fun, fun di,

00:11:31.498 --> 00:11:32.828
funem holts.

00:11:32.828 --> 00:11:34.546
un dortn ze'mir gevezn

00:11:34.671 --> 00:11:38.023
un m'hot gearbet, un ven m'hot gedorfn geyn nokh esn,

00:11:38.023 --> 00:11:40.498
ze'mir gegangen in, in, in di derfer mit zey.

00:11:40.498 --> 00:11:43.451
un a por mol ze'mir gegangen oyf ZADANyes,

00:11:43.451 --> 00:11:47.445
dort vu eyn bruder fun dem bokher hot men avekgeharget dortn,

00:11:47.445 --> 00:11:48.418
di daytshn.

00:11:48.947 --> 00:11:50.915
un azoy ze'm- vayl...

00:11:49.808 --> 00:11:51.067
in shlakht?

00:11:51.327 --> 00:11:52.384
in shlakht.

00:11:52.423 --> 00:11:54.357
vayl m'hot gegangen nemen aheym,

00:11:54.465 --> 00:11:56.968
s'iz geven dort hundert, di VLASOVTSes,

00:11:56.968 --> 00:12:00.517
vos zenen g- vos zenen geven ongetun mit daytshishe ongetun un zey hobn gevolt antloyfn

00:12:00.895 --> 00:12:02.343
in di partizan⟨er⟩.

00:12:02.343 --> 00:12:04.632
ze'mir gegangen, m'hot ongenumen firn mit,

00:12:04.632 --> 00:12:06.694
mit tsuker, mit vos m'hot getrofn.

00:12:06.970 --> 00:12:09.498
un m'iz geven, tsurikgeforn in otryad arayn,

00:12:09.498 --> 00:12:11.514
ober dem bokher mit nokh eyn b-,

00:12:11.514 --> 00:12:13.714
krist, zenen geharget gevorn dortn

00:12:13.888 --> 00:12:16.194
barn shlakht ven m'hot zikh geshlogn mit di daytshn.

00:12:16.842 --> 00:12:20.008
⟨un⟩ ze'mir tsurikgekumen, un dort bin ikh gevezn

00:12:20.402 --> 00:12:21.543
biz

00:12:22.377 --> 00:12:24.024
fir un fertsik,

00:12:25.296 --> 00:12:27.163
AUGUST, dakht zikh ⟨mir⟩, iz dos gevezn.

00:12:27.287 --> 00:12:30.268
di VLASOVTSes zaynen gekumen in ayer otryad?

00:12:29.835 --> 00:12:30.588
ye.

00:12:30.477 --> 00:12:32.593
un zaynen gevorn partizanen?

00:12:32.485 --> 00:12:34.099
m'hot zey gegibn gever,

00:12:34.324 --> 00:12:37.625
un zey ⟨zenen⟩ geven mit undz. ober zey zenen gegangen mit daytshish⟨er⟩ ongetun,

00:12:37.885 --> 00:12:38.890
shineln.

00:12:38.890 --> 00:12:41.338
zenen ge-, zey hobn geshikt eynem in otryad,

00:12:41.479 --> 00:12:43.565
er zol zogn az zey viln antloyfn.

00:12:44.348 --> 00:12:47.126
un zey v- ⟨nor⟩ zey veysn, zey hobn moyre, zey veysn nisht vu.

00:12:47.503 --> 00:12:50.990
un ven m'iz ongefaln di daytshn, zenen zey geshtanen ⟨in der⟩ vakh,

00:12:51.908 --> 00:12:54.011
hobn zey nisht geshosn oyf di mentshn.

00:12:54.945 --> 00:12:56.899
un di daytshn zenen dort antlofn,

00:12:56.899 --> 00:13:00.296
un dem andern tog,... nokh dem hot men dertseylt, shoyn nokh der milkhome,

00:13:00.296 --> 00:13:03.906
az di tsvey partizaner hobn gehongen oyfn TELEFONNYY stolb:

00:13:04.716 --> 00:13:06.110
der yid mit di,

00:13:06.201 --> 00:13:07.410
mit dem krist.

00:13:09.140 --> 00:13:10.987
⟨d-⟩ dort ze'mir gevezn

00:13:12.023 --> 00:13:13.063
biz

00:13:13.913 --> 00:13:15.425
fir un fertsik,

00:13:16.950 --> 00:13:18.091
AUGUST,

00:13:19.043 --> 00:13:20.269
un dernokh dem,

00:13:21.507 --> 00:13:23.284
zey hobn undz ale genumen,

00:13:23.284 --> 00:13:24.789
un ze'mir avekgegan

00:13:24.789 --> 00:13:25.956
frayvilik

00:13:27.565 --> 00:13:28.811
oyfn front.

00:13:28.811 --> 00:13:32.689
zey hobn gezogt az mir ze'mir shoyn nisht vayt. m'iz sh- der front iz shoyn geven in Poyln,

00:13:32.914 --> 00:13:35.895
un me muz yetst geyn endikn di milkhome.

00:13:36.677 --> 00:13:39.860
bin ikh oykh gegangen un di por yidn zenen gegangen.

00:13:41.487 --> 00:13:46.155
un ze'mir, un azoy hot men undz gefirt nokh Brest-Litovsk ariber dem Bug,

00:13:46.380 --> 00:13:48.517
un avekgefirt hundert kilometer.

00:13:50.532 --> 00:13:52.230
un dortn hot men undz

00:13:53.788 --> 00:13:56.583
gegibn ander ontun, V- militerish,

00:13:56.725 --> 00:13:58.035
mit a biks,

00:13:58.075 --> 00:13:59.587
un m'hot undz gefirt

00:14:00.285 --> 00:14:03.536
oyf der ershter linye, vayl zey hobn gevust az mir ze'mir partizanen,

00:14:05.044 --> 00:14:08.328
iz ken'mir shisn, hot men undz avekgefirt teykef oyf der ershter linye.

00:14:08.520 --> 00:14:10.606
ikh bin opgeven dort nisht lang.

00:14:10.967 --> 00:14:12.010
ikh bin geven

00:14:12.010 --> 00:14:13.492
a SVYAZIST

00:14:13.870 --> 00:14:16.176
un ikh bin gegangen farrikhtn dem telefon.

00:14:17.886 --> 00:14:20.669
tsi s'iz geven a mine, tsi mit, mit a ⟨b-⟩

00:14:20.856 --> 00:14:22.086
SNARYAD,

00:14:22.459 --> 00:14:23.465
hot mir

00:14:24.349 --> 00:14:27.093
getrofn un hot mir farvundet di, ⟨⟩,

00:14:27.100 --> 00:14:29.524
di hant, beyde hent, un di fis,

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:31.380
un ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent

00:14:31.774 --> 00:14:33.388
zayn tsurik in der armey.

00:14:33.597 --> 00:14:37.472
bin ikh avekgegangen in, in di, vu s'iz geven di tshast,

00:14:37.647 --> 00:14:39.210
un dortn hot men mir

00:14:39.250 --> 00:14:40.425
farbundn

00:14:41.292 --> 00:14:44.323
mit a drot di hant, vayl s'iz nisht geven mit vos tsu farbindn.

00:14:44.852 --> 00:14:47.124
un bay nakht hot men mir avekgefirt

00:14:49.257 --> 00:14:52.373
dortn oyf eyn plats, un m'hot mir gevolt opshnaydn di hant.

00:14:52.632 --> 00:14:55.453
hob ikh shtark gebetn, az me zol mir nisht opshnaydn di hant, vayl ikh b-

00:14:55.453 --> 00:14:57.609
ikh bin geblibn eyner; s'iz keyner nishto.

00:14:57.609 --> 00:14:58.734
vos zol ikh tun?

00:14:59.061 --> 00:15:02.362
hot men mir arumgeleygt a gips un zey hobn gezogt "BOG S NIM."

00:15:03.364 --> 00:15:06.412
dernokh dem hot men mir avekgefirt keyn Brest-Litovsk

00:15:06.570 --> 00:15:07.914
in a HOSPITAL.

00:15:08.106 --> 00:15:10.310
er't mir dortn nokh a mol operirt,

00:15:10.502 --> 00:15:12.321
un aroyfgeleygt nokh a mol a gips,

00:15:12.321 --> 00:15:14.310
un fun dortn mit a

00:15:14.367 --> 00:15:15.660
SANITARN⟨YY⟩

00:15:15.852 --> 00:15:18.708
ban, hot men mir avekgefirt biz keyn Saratov.

00:15:19.412 --> 00:15:21.869
az ir zayt gevezn in partizanen,

00:15:22.011 --> 00:15:26.544
iz, hot ir gefilt dortn a- dem antisemitizm? gevezn...?

00:15:26.179 --> 00:15:27.877
o, dos fargesn tsu dertseyln.

00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:29.649
ven i- ven m'hot undz

00:15:29.655 --> 00:15:31.758
geshlogn in di partizanen,

00:15:31.917 --> 00:15:34.746
bay VOROSHILOV's, m'hot undz geharget un geshlogn,

00:15:35.089 --> 00:15:37.631
iz geshtanen eyner in der zayt mit a biks.

00:15:37.924 --> 00:15:40.215
hot er tsvey verter gezogt oyf yidish:

00:15:40.215 --> 00:15:42.524
"hots nisht moyre; m'vet aykh nisht derhargenen.

00:15:43.408 --> 00:15:45.055
mit yedn kumt azoy."

00:15:45.265 --> 00:15:47.250
un mer hot er gornisht gevolt redn.

00:15:48.893 --> 00:15:50.237
un s'iz geven a yid

00:15:50.395 --> 00:15:51.531
far vos,

00:15:50.412 --> 00:15:51.739
in yenem otryad.

00:15:51.531 --> 00:15:53.122
far vos hobn zey aykh geshlogn?

00:15:53.179 --> 00:15:55.204
zey hobn geshrign az ze'mir shpyonen.

00:15:55.795 --> 00:15:57.864
⟨undz⟩ ze'mir geven bay di daytshn shpyonen.

00:16:00.958 --> 00:16:04.085
un dem, in dem naye⟨n⟩ otryad, vu m'hot aykh ongenumen,

00:16:04.085 --> 00:16:06.116
hot ir gefilt antisemitizm?

00:16:06.088 --> 00:16:09.980
NO. keyn yidn, hobn mir nisht getrofn dort. nisht geven.

00:16:10.459 --> 00:16:13.965
un aykh vi yidn hot, vi hot zikh tsu aykh batsoygn der komandir,

00:16:13.965 --> 00:16:15.228
di andere?

00:16:14.222 --> 00:16:15.616
zeyer gut.

00:16:15.808 --> 00:16:20.729
un ikh hob gea-, dort vu, bay dem vos kh'hob gearbet, iz oykhet geven a shtikl komandir,

00:16:21.276 --> 00:16:22.429
zeyer gut.

00:16:22.429 --> 00:16:25.320
er fleg mir shikn, ikh zol im nemen, brengen esn,

00:16:25.343 --> 00:16:28.273
vayl er iz geven a shtikl ofitser; ofitser hot men gegibn

00:16:29.089 --> 00:16:30.213
beser esn.

00:16:30.827 --> 00:16:35.884
un, un ikh hob gearbet, gemakht di, tsu di biksn, di prikladn.

00:16:35.991 --> 00:16:38.384
un dos hobn shoyn gehat, mentshn

00:16:38.384 --> 00:16:39.816
tsu nemen a biks.

00:16:40.125 --> 00:16:44.051
un ikh hob gehat a biks mit a GUN, un arumgebundn mit granatn.

00:16:44.445 --> 00:16:47.746
un, shtendik gehaltn zikh a, a f- a naye pulye:

00:16:47.871 --> 00:16:49.654
bald ⟨veln⟩ di daytshn mir khapn,

00:16:49.862 --> 00:16:51.560
zol ikh zikh teykef shisn.

00:16:52.917 --> 00:16:56.031
vayl ikh hob ⟨sh-⟩, nisht gevolt araynfaln tsu di daytshishe hent arayn.

00:16:56.031 --> 00:16:56.811
kh'hob gevust

00:16:56.811 --> 00:16:59.036
vos s'vet mir kumen alts a partizan.

00:17:00.190 --> 00:17:04.470
un in der armey, hot ir gefilt antisemitizm

00:17:04.560 --> 00:17:08.081
tsu, ⟨hot men⟩, vi hot men zikh tsu aykh batsoygn az ir zayt shoyn geven in a- in der armey?

00:17:09.538 --> 00:17:11.877
neyn. UNK ikh bin nisht lang geven in der armey.

00:17:12.373 --> 00:17:15.809
kh'bin dort geven, nisht gev-, m'hot nisht gevust dortn tsi ikh bin a yid.

00:17:16.541 --> 00:17:18.276
nor ven s'hot mir geranyet,

00:17:18.276 --> 00:17:19.588
hobn zey gezogt,

00:17:21.402 --> 00:17:23.483
"TY B-", "TY BYL SONNYY."

00:17:23.483 --> 00:17:25.817
"bist geven farshlofn. vi ⟨azoy bi⟩stu popadyet

00:17:26.396 --> 00:17:27.689
in der armey arayn?

00:17:27.780 --> 00:17:31.160
di yidn zenen zikh in mitl-, Azye.

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:33.140
mit a krumer biks shi⟨k⟩sn zey."

00:17:35.695 --> 00:17:41.708
azoy zayt ir ge- a farvundeter UNK zayt ir gebrakht, gebrakht gevorn keyn Saratov, ye?

00:17:41.213 --> 00:17:43.012
yo. in Saratov

00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:45.358
iz geven nokh demolst vinter,

00:17:45.482 --> 00:17:47.096
un dortn hot men mir

00:17:47.136 --> 00:17:49.354
nokh a mol operirt di ander hant,

00:17:49.549 --> 00:17:51.115
un dortn bin ikh gelign,

00:17:51.115 --> 00:17:53.182
un dort iz geven yidishe

00:17:53.182 --> 00:17:56.034
doktoyrim. ⟨der, der⟩ natshalnik iz geven yidn.

00:17:56.034 --> 00:17:57.406
m'hot mir zeyer

00:17:58.695 --> 00:17:59.814
lib gehat,

00:17:59.814 --> 00:18:04.021
vayl kh'bin geven der shverster farvundeter fun ale. kh'hob nisht gekent geyn; ikh bin nor gelign.

00:18:05.226 --> 00:18:07.380
hot men mir ge- oysgeshribn

00:18:07.572 --> 00:18:08.969
vays broyt.

00:18:08.969 --> 00:18:11.189
m'hot mir oysgeshribn a shtikl puter,

00:18:11.189 --> 00:18:13.315
mer vi andere.

00:18:13.315 --> 00:18:17.303
m'hot mir gegibn a bisl bronfn, ikh zol trinken, zol zikh kenen shteln oyf di fis.

00:18:17.882 --> 00:18:19.597
un dortn bin ikh geven

00:18:21.342 --> 00:18:23.209
ven s'iz geven shoyn di POBEDY.

00:18:24.109 --> 00:18:29.081
dernokh dem hot men likvidir- genumen likvidirn dem HOSPITAL. ikh hob nisht gehat vu tsu forn.

00:18:29.644 --> 00:18:32.270
hob ikh gezogt dem natshalnik, "ikh hob nisht vu tsu forn,

00:18:32.935 --> 00:18:35.460
vayl ⟨k-⟩ ale ⟨y-⟩ oysgeharget. vu zol ikh forn?"

00:18:36.175 --> 00:18:39.597
un derno- hot er mir gezogt, "hob nisht moyre; du vest kenen zayn do.

00:18:39.597 --> 00:18:41.298
bay undz vestu arbetn."

00:18:42.503 --> 00:18:45.737
ober dernokh dem hob ikh gehert az me fort, di yidn, keyn Poyln.

00:18:46.367 --> 00:18:48.285
hob ikh geklert, "ikh'l forn keyn Poyln."

00:18:49.742 --> 00:18:52.503
hobn zey mir gegibn a TICKET keyn Poyln, keyn Khelem,

00:18:52.932 --> 00:18:54.565
ober ikh bin tsugeforn biz

00:18:54.565 --> 00:18:57.583
LYUBOML', vayl dort geyt di stantsye. hob ikh geklert, "neyn.

00:18:57.623 --> 00:18:59.974
lomikh aropgeyn gibn a kuk,

00:18:59.974 --> 00:19:01.953
efsher emetser iz geblibn fun di yidn,

00:19:02.128 --> 00:19:04.940
fun der m- efsher emetser fun der mishpokhe, efsher emetser."

00:19:05.200 --> 00:19:06.476
⟨az m'hot⟩ gekumen, ⟨i-⟩

00:19:06.651 --> 00:19:08.265
iz nor geven a por,

00:19:08.575 --> 00:19:10.889
fun di derfer, a por yidn hobn gevoynt,

00:19:10.889 --> 00:19:12.180
un keyner iz nisht geven.

00:19:12.743 --> 00:19:14.526
un ikh hob nisht gehat afile

00:19:14.937 --> 00:19:16.291
vu tsu shlofn.

00:19:16.405 --> 00:19:19.793
dernokh dem iz geven dort eyner m- mit, on a fus, a invalid,

00:19:19.793 --> 00:19:20.887
a bakanter,

00:19:21.518 --> 00:19:23.014
oykhet Melamed,

00:19:23.273 --> 00:19:26.473
ober nisht keyn mishpokhe, a bakanter. er iz geven mayn bruder's khaver.

00:19:26.698 --> 00:19:30.404
un er hot, er hot gehat eyn kleyn tsimerl, iz er geven mit a froy mit a kind.

00:19:30.495 --> 00:19:34.204
un er hot mir arayngenumen in dem tsimerl, un ikh ⟨bin⟩ geven bay zey dortn.

00:19:36.300 --> 00:19:40.344
zogt mir, di milkhome hot zikh geendikt, di krig hot zikh geendikt;

00:19:40.806 --> 00:19:44.867
ve- ver fun ayer, mishpokhe iz umgekumen?

00:19:46.155 --> 00:19:48.444
ir hot gehat brider, shvester;

00:19:48.636 --> 00:19:50.486
vos iz forgekumen mit zey?

00:19:51.555 --> 00:19:54.393
mayn bruder mit nokh eynem fun Opalin...

00:19:54.393 --> 00:19:56.528
hobn dernokh dem dertseylt, nokh der milkhome...

00:19:56.989 --> 00:19:59.902
iz er, er hot gearbet dortn baym porets

00:19:59.959 --> 00:20:04.470
in Zabuzhe. iz er antlofn mitn bokher, zenen aribergeshvumen dem taykh, dem Bug,

00:20:04.470 --> 00:20:05.809
in der anderer zayt.

00:20:06.102 --> 00:20:07.986
di daytshn hobn zey gekhapt,

00:20:08.295 --> 00:20:10.803
un m'hot zey tsurik aribergebrengt, un m'hot zey geshosn.

00:20:10.776 --> 00:20:13.217
vi, velkher bruder iz dos geven? vi hot er geheysn?

00:20:12.683 --> 00:20:13.605
Refoel.

00:20:15.180 --> 00:20:19.595
un, in Opalin hot men geshosn mayn shvester, Miryem,

00:20:21.238 --> 00:20:24.387
geshosn di, Refoel's vayb mitn kind,

00:20:25.862 --> 00:20:27.192
un geshosn

00:20:27.192 --> 00:20:30.210
dem onkl's froy mitn kind,

00:20:30.317 --> 00:20:34.125
un im, ⟨un⟩ mayn, onkl mit dray zin.

00:20:35.565 --> 00:20:39.237
er iz gevezn in, bay a krist farbahaltn,

00:20:39.598 --> 00:20:42.039
biz tsvey vokhn far der milkhome.

00:20:42.788 --> 00:20:46.747
dernokh dem hot men im gefunen dortn, un m'hot zey aroysgenumen, m'hot zey geshosn

00:20:46.956 --> 00:20:47.992
in vald.

00:20:47.715 --> 00:20:50.240
zaynen geven bahaltn vu? in Apolin?

00:20:49.690 --> 00:20:50.612
in Opalin,

00:20:50.871 --> 00:20:52.046
bay a krist.

00:20:51.917 --> 00:20:53.463
ir veyst zayn nomen?

00:20:53.807 --> 00:20:56.157
kh'hob gevust; kh'hob im gekent. ⟨JASKI⟩.

00:20:56.794 --> 00:20:59.653
UNK dernokh dem hot men im genumen oyfn front un er iz geharget gevorn.

00:20:59.653 --> 00:21:01.126
dos hot er gehat batsolt.

00:21:01.806 --> 00:21:03.827
un dos vayb hob ikh gezen, az ikh bin geven,

00:21:03.827 --> 00:21:06.929
ikh bin gekumen in finef un fertsikstn yor, hob ikh zi getrofn, hob ikh zi gezen.

00:21:11.273 --> 00:21:13.865
